      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING FRITZ (3) has hit the frame in both career runs, the latest when third (17.91) over 324m at this track. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Close to a win and looks a key chance. ADRIFT (8) was a course and distance placegetter (18.07) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 0.8 lengths second in a Maiden. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. GO FORWARD TOMMY (1) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 4.5 lengths behind Chasing Kisses in 18.12 and recording a new PB here. Will be in this for a long way. WHODAT MUSTANG (2) is a last-start placegetter in a tight finish – sure to have admirers.",
